s_synopsis: Down below, the enemy sit unaware while a seek, black jet slices through the dark. No blips appear on the radar, no signs are given. Then, in an instant, the roar of exploding ordinance shatters the night, demolishing targets, sending troops and pilots scrambling. As quickly as it appeared, the menacing airborne apparition vanishes into the night sky. The F-117A has just come calling.
